T16TD4414E:349b-1: tri ratna mangga la g'a th'a /
T16TD4414E:350a-1: mchog gsum gyi bkra shis kyi tshigs su bcad pa /
T16TD4414E:350a-2: dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
T16TD4414E:350a-3: rgya mtsho lta bur brgal dka' 'khor ba'i 'dam las rgal //
T16TD4414E:350a-4: bsod nams ye shes tshogs gnyis bsags dka' ma lus rdzogs /
T16TD4414E:350a-5: 'gro ba kun gyi gnyen gcig gyur pa de bzhin gshegs //
T16TD4414E:350a-6: bkra shis dam pa des kyang der 'dir bde legs shog / rang don spangs shing gzhan don rtag tu lhur len cing //
T16TD4414E:350a-7: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga la lta ba rgyang bsrings te //
T16TD4414E:350a-8: dad dang brtson 'grus lhur len grags mchog byang chub sems //
T16TD4414E:350a-9: bkra shis dam pa des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog / skye 'gag med cing rtog pa'i 'ching byed mtha' dag spangs //
T16TD4414E:350a-10: ma rig mun pa 'joms byed stong nyid sgron ma'i mchog / dmigs pa sna tshogs spangs pa lam gyi bde sgrub chos //
T16TD4414E:350a-11: bkra shis dam pa des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog //
T16TD4414E:350a-12: dkon mchog gsum gyi bkra shis kyi tshigs su bcad pa rdzogs so /
